{"tid":1640580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"破壞個站，俾你影到，仲用胡椒噴霧？","createTime":"2019-10-09T04:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T04:58:39.000Z","uid":132999,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d53adf6982a648d1a6b7d9f77b3629fca49ceb","tid":1640580,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:26:26.000Z","msg":"件事係咪真係咁單純？啲狗 on9？<br />\n<br />\n定係佢哋特登做俾你睇？特以後一有手足拆鐵/裝修就俾人話係鬼？甚至俾人屌？配合番近帶風向去分化和理非同前線？或者佢哋已經背後已經有壓力叫佢哋解決裝修問題？<br />\n<br />\n其實無論係咪都好，大家記住兩個守則：<br />\n1. 留意警惕就得，唔好捉鬼<br />\n2. 核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\n最後就算有狗出黎幫手，咁咪由得佢幫囉！"},{"pid":"18ff4b8d5b1d1b6f5cab376b43e223b6be4403ee","tid":1640580,"uid":41530,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:30:35.000Z","msg":"其實啲狗真係咁撚蠢嫁，唔蠢點做狗？"},{"pid":"b7210177306cdfd2769fca406a993c208edcddc2","tid":1640580,"uid":266668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:31:10.000Z","msg":"純粹蠢啫"},{"pid":"64fb67de7e935d485dd71bfdd447795e8d738f60","tid":1640580,"uid":18639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"佢地慣左咁做 潛意識就係出椒嚇走左你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3e747bbc53f5c51c023ceca4c3567aeee53f4c","tid":1640580,"uid":65556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:35:30.000Z","msg":"真係蠢 扮唔到"},{"pid":"31858d0c99e9caa891a1a42ba2a2304b2871798d","tid":1640580,"uid":258285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:36:47.000Z","msg":"做緊任務唔使捉鬼，提防下就得啦。<br />\n事後文宣篤鬼"},{"pid":"43074e461a471fbc7a45905bc163849a66519dc1","tid":1640580,"uid":132999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"18ff4b8d5b1d1b6f5cab376b43e223b6be4403ee","tid":1640580,"uid":41530,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:30:35.000Z","msg":"其實啲狗真係咁撚蠢嫁，唔蠢點做狗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:41:12.000Z","msg":"佢哋背後有咁多陰險之徒<br />\n<br />\n係唔係都好，重點係核彈都唔割！"},{"pid":"8ce5621ca1ae10d7